    <h4>Blinded or Complete Darkness</h4>
    
    <p>A blinded character is at a three dice penalty to any and every task that requires vision including attacking and defending.</p>
    
    <h4>Deafened</h4>
    
    <p>The character cannot hear anything and should be penalised if they act on information they shouldn't have.</p>
    
    <h4>Flanking</h4>
    
    <p>Does nothing.  Fighting ability is paramount.</p>